# Greenland Situation Monitor - API Configuration
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your API keys

# ============================================
# REQUIRED APIs (Free tier available)
# ============================================

# Finnhub API - Stock market data
# Get your free key at: https://finnhub.io/
# Used for: Market indices, sector performance
VITE_FINNHUB_API_KEY=your_finnhub_api_key_here

# FRED API - Federal Reserve Economic Data
# Get your free key at: https://fred.stlouisfed.org/docs/api/api_key.html
# Used for: Fed indicators, interest rates, treasury yields
VITE_FRED_API_KEY=your_fred_api_key_here

# ============================================
# NO API KEY REQUIRED (Public APIs)
# ============================================

# GDELT API - Global news events
# No key required - public API
# Used for: Primary news feed across all categories

# CoinGecko API - Cryptocurrency prices
# No key required for basic tier (rate limited)
# Used for: Crypto panel prices

# Polymarket Gamma API - Prediction markets
# No key required - public API
# Used for: Betting odds panel

# Kalshi API - Prediction markets
# No key required for public market data
# Used for: Betting odds panel

# ============================================
# OPTIONAL APIs (Premium features)
# ============================================

# Whale Alert API - Large crypto transactions
# Get your key at: https://whale-alert.io/
# Used for: Whale transactions panel (currently disabled)
# VITE_WHALE_ALERT_API_KEY=your_whale_alert_key_here

# ============================================
# CORS PROXY CONFIGURATION
# ============================================

# The app uses a Cloudflare Worker CORS proxy for RSS feeds
# Default proxy is configured in src/lib/config/api.ts
# You can deploy your own proxy and set the URL here:
# VITE_CORS_PROXY_URL=https://your-cors-proxy.workers.dev

# ============================================
# API STATUS
# ============================================
#
# Working without keys:
# - GDELT news API
# - CoinGecko crypto prices
# - Polymarket predictions
# - Kalshi predictions
# - Open-Meteo weather (map tooltips)
#
# Requires API key:
# - Finnhub (markets, sectors)
# - FRED (Fed indicators)
#
# Disabled/Empty:
# - Whale Alert (needs premium key)
# - Gov Contracts (needs implementation)
# - Layoffs data (no public API)
